          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Realistic Timeline</h3>
      <p>Standard board resolutions (1-2 pages) complete in 2-4 hours. Multiple resolutions or complex meeting minutes may need 6-12 hours. If you have a bank appointment scheduled, tell us the date. We prioritize to ensure you have the translation ready.</p>

